        "subject": "LU-11476 lnd: Update health status for ECONNRESET",
        "message": "LU-11476 lnd: Update health status for ECONNRESET\n\nIn ksocknal_txlist_done(), ECONNRESET error is not\naccounted for and thus the tx health status is wrongly\nupdated to LNET_MSG_STATUS_LOCAL_ERROR for this error.\n\nAccount for this error and update the tx health status\nto LNET_MSG_STATUS_REMOTE_DROPPED.\n\nChange-Id: I54ec51c6270b66db75865ecbf41b47a4912e21fd\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Sonia Sharma <sharmaso@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
